subject: Soccer
Football Association Cup (Soccer)
lead_paragraph: Liverpool dispatched fourth-tier Exeter in the F.A. Cup, with the reserves Sheyi Ojo and Joao Carlos Teixeira scoring their first goals to help the club complete a 3-0 third-round victory at home.
